Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than fifty years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there were seven men
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who fought and survived
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the burning depths of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three things kept them going:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,courage, guts, and their bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seven of them placed their hopes on the seven-coloured rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they swore that they would definitely survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it is hard to make out now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What they desired is certainly engraved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:00:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were the dreams of the seven men.
