Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.12,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years have passed since the end of the Second World War.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.62,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Japan has not yet economically recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:24.79,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Homeless are appearing everywhere. Almost everyone is experiencing poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:29.63,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The catastrophe is even affecting innocent women and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.22,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,They can only accept things as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:37.47,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,In such cruel times, these 6 boys were sent to a juvenile prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:43.69,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}Like fallen leaves being carried by the flow of their surroundings, they're being forced to face their uncertain futures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:45.89,Default,police,0000,0000,0000,,Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.25,Default,police,0000,0000,0000,,These are the 6 new guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.47,Default,police,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of them, Dr Sasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:54.82,Default,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sasaki, the medic responsible for overseeing this facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:58.66,Default,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,A healthy body will ensure a good future, so please look after yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:00.56,Default,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:07.86,Default,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,It will be simple and quick, so there is no need to be so tense. Please, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.05,Default,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.19,Default,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:19.89,Default,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,It will be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:23.42,Default,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Right then. Let's start with you over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.76,Default,police,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow. How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:40.26,Default,police,0000,0000,0000,,So this good for nothing punk still has some shame within him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.94,Default,police,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get out,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.46,Default,police,0000,0000,0000,,you stupid fatfuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:49.58,Default,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Pleas stop that, Ishihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:54.00,Default,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can forgive you if you harm any of these boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.20,Default,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:06:00.57,Default,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you, the blue eyed boy.
