Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:11.99,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,These boys were treated like slaves just for the guards' perverted pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.22,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,They could do nothing about it.
