Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.87,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of the kind of person subject to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.28,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,they would feel ashamed and violated by that treatment.
