Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:03.19,Default,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ehm....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:06.40,Default,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Could you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:08.63,Default,guy,0000,0000,0000,,tell us your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:14.66,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you are all just punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.97,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,You should first give your own name,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:22.23,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,before asking for another's, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:25.62,Default,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:28.50,Default,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:29.88,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:35.83,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,Have a quick puff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:44.10,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,We should not smoke alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:51.62,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I want to hear your names.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:52.93,Default,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.13,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,Take a puff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:04.24,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,You're the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:07.67,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take over the watching, so hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.30,Default,guy,0000,0000,0000,,You want to bribe us all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:13.08,Default,guy,0000,0000,0000,,with just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:23.05,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,Bribing six punks? What's in for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:32.47,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the kind of problems you boys went through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:46.16,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, its almost finished, smoke it while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:07.22,Default,guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:21.30,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sakuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:25.16,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi Rokurouta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:26.33,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:37.79,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully, in two summers time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.96,Default,Sakuragi,0000,0000,0000,,everyone will regain their freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:48.87,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:50.94,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi Rokurouta
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.05,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,standing up like an older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:59.74,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,A brother who's kind and protecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.62,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,These boys where not familiar with the feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:06.74,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,the feeling that this kind hearted brother was expressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:10.16,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,That feeling might vanish from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:12.41,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,But here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:17.17,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,the feeling of a rainbow marked on their hearts will prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:24.32,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,What could I keep watching over
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:30.66,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,with these empty eyes of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:36.24,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:41.00,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,my life for those whom I must protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:45.34,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,He pulled me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:47.56,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep on flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:53.14,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So far away, but I'll never give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:59.66,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Our unbreakable bond
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:05.87,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,has begun to entwine with fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:12.42,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,guiding us to the endless future laid out before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:21.36,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will get all warm inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:26.02,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,A far-off distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:31.96,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:34.83,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,It connotes hopping away, thus it is referred as "rabbit".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:36.42,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Joe runs...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:38.46,Default,narrator,0000,0000,0000,,to see his sister.
